{"tid":47240,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"［完美主義JJ] 會買書睇既巴打入","createTime":"2016-12-20T08:07:07.000Z","updateTime":"2016-12-23T01:37:33.000Z","uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa223bb75bae8e0a1decb58ac10c06c929a2b454","tid":47240,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:07:07.000Z","msg":"岩岩去書店想買書睇<br />\n但發現本本現貨都殘殘地<br />\n因為睇過少少內容都覺得唔錯 所以好想買<br />\n之後我就打電話去其他分店問有無貨<br />\n佢地話有，<br />\n問佢新唔新淨<br />\n佢話本本都唔新淨<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後諗左好耐 因為真係好想睇<br />\n先屈服到自己買本有啲殘既書<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n殘既程度係 <br />\n書皮啲角位有啲分開左咁<br />\n封面有啲花<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5bd66ddc8bdb111d27c23fdd05c43086295c6cc8","tid":47240,"uid":90,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:09:25.000Z","msg":"我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定慢慢搵到完美冇事嘅先買"},{"pid":"150f5c0441ba654459711acdef6748962e4ece53","tid":47240,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T08:43:22.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一定慢慢搵到完美冇事嘅先買</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n頭先係咁說服自己睇耐左都會殘<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4d57bb9e004873994522d76d18f79b7fa3744c","tid":47240,"uid":51389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-20T15:36:56.000Z","msg":"如果要買殘既「新書」情願唔買 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a41a7c02a04330ac1db7e920863b591a6b440ad1","tid":47240,"uid":29737,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T05:14:19.000Z","msg":"有d捨本逐末<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 又唔係董橋果d整到靚一靚用來收藏嘅書"},{"pid":"e2e68449a3bcce563a9d3eb65115482f745d15ea","tid":47240,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:52:36.000Z","msg":"有嘅話，會買有膠套包住嘅<br />\n雖然係唔環保"},{"pid":"57228f92ea6fba24aea8f785fc7dacebed3612a1","tid":47240,"uid":68192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T06:55:53.000Z","msg":"同埋會睇下本書有無被人屈過 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c730af9c93463df9f67f32d4d2f0d3ecf0a82d5c","tid":47240,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T13:16:15.000Z","msg":"我就冇乜所謂，好睇ok，殘少少接受到"},{"pid":"7d9a438096597ec0aec32ab8010a40f0cfadc96a","tid":47240,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T16:44:15.000Z","msg":"唔嫌貴不如去誠品買<br />\n實有貨<br />\n有心機嘅去二樓書店買都得啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"489a5ccd013968cbaeb2c25eb791e72b8a1c4084","tid":47240,"uid":41315,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:01:07.000Z","msg":"我屋企有接近100本書<br />\n基本上買既每本書都接近完美先買<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n雖然睇下睇下點都會有啲殘<br />\n但未買就殘左過唔到自己果關"},{"pid":"8c4464e28d34efa2f5634cf46a5a2e60f9f479d7","tid":47240,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:23:15.000Z","msg":"你地會唔會自己包書，同埋應該點keep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb80180f9d9b50b8e62511a1a5ed92672b1e4b94","tid":47240,"uid":45400,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T17:25:34.000Z","msg":"我都係咁 揀勁耐要搵本最接近100%完美<br />\n<br />\n通常問sales拎本未拆封既先<br />\n<br />\n而且大量書未睇都係要買返屋企，根本睇唔撚切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8fee717331bbca4f84547cf6bc8b080d43063b0d","tid":47240,"uid":43422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:32:50.000Z","msg":"有時揀到本靚仔到不得了既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一返到去撕價錢牌就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係樓上書店有得慢慢揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59de4e2a6f5e86fba034335e3c15f60c940f2c2a","tid":47240,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:40:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地會唔會自己包書，同埋應該點keep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n用透明包書膠<br />\n平時放入有門的書櫃就算"},{"pid":"340a4c00cbc612dfe44150bc2312789c76ca3e86","tid":47240,"uid":38218,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:42:20.000Z","msg":"依家較多上網買<br />\nBook Depository<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bookdepository.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bookdepository.com&d=yAza6%2BG8uP2PGvR%2Bc5vk3ksIbL4fERhwM0ZRx9Zc9p0%3D&h=4364399f\" target=\"_blank\">http://www.bookdepository.com</a>"},{"pid":"5fccaca9dd74e67dd1f0f1c65568a8970eacb49a","tid":47240,"uid":60540,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-21T18:42:25.000Z","msg":"多數上網訂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b407eff07ab0a688714f94d50d6f4e5fb0baeb0c","tid":47240,"uid":49974,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:11:29.000Z","msg":"本書就咁擺係房幾日就變成咁，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w4xz69yd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw4xz69yd&h=9c4cafb6&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b860799dc5f8862524fe54f02f9ba39a5ed3063f","tid":47240,"uid":25232,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:26:24.000Z","msg":"以前係<br />\n但係而家求兼有得睇都OK,<br />\n屋企9成二手書"},{"pid":"45941818e965e444b42b33422ac429dd44ca58bd","tid":47240,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:38:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你地會唔會自己包書，同埋應該點keep<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我以前啲小說有自己包<br />\n但近年好懶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過有啲書好耐無睇又無掂，有啲變黃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d4948acb8718f77838ab8c6aed66a7acec6bb7ef","tid":47240,"uid":60682,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T03:39:03.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我都係咁 揀勁耐要搵本最接近100%完美<br />\n<br />\n通常問sales拎本未拆封既先<br />\n<br />\n而且大量書未睇都係要買返屋企，根本睇唔撚切<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 幾年前係書展買果啲我都未睇晒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"90f37d793f7bf16b74217fa0ff80a61271aa87a5","tid":47240,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:01:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>本書就咁擺係房幾日就變成咁，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w4xz69yd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw4xz69yd&h=9c4cafb6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏天有開冷氣嘅時候，就算揭都未揭都會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9815c36b0cdfd9902b92ae928c5c6e2c34b42f54","tid":47240,"uid":43880,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:04:37.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時揀到本靚仔到不得了既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一返到去撕價錢牌就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係樓上書店有得慢慢揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n撕價錢牌要好高技巧<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 衰過幾次之後而加費事撕<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n樓上書店每本書只擺一本，邊有得揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"dd18caa1708a41205bf657b31ef4b4f87ea23985","tid":47240,"uid":11618,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T04:16:31.000Z","msg":"除非爛得好嚴重<br />\n要不然都會照買 反正用來睇<br />\n前排係屋企執書，有成六個紙皮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n仲諗緊點處置佢地"},{"pid":"62039c484437b4761a454726a4a63f9f71138ec8","tid":47240,"uid":24227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:30:19.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>本書就咁擺係房幾日就變成咁，可以點做<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://holland.pk/w4xz69yd\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2Fw4xz69yd&h=9c4cafb6&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n夏天有開冷氣嘅時候，就算揭都未揭都會變成咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n應該係潮濕"},{"pid":"7f0a3497938c4a39ee41aca6baf51d4b3ef0d68b","tid":47240,"uid":62030,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2016-12-22T10:42:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有時揀到本靚仔到不得了既<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一返到去撕價錢牌就出事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n係樓上書店有得慢慢揀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n張貼紙要用風筒吹半分鐘到一分鐘熱哂再撕"}]}